https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tu0uRulqcnPnbmgu0giNH0Vl5vZ.jpg Barbara is about to travel to Spain for an exhibition of her paintings. The night before starting her journey there is a hurricane and she has to stay in a nightclub until the morning. During the night she comes into contact with different people who have a variety of conflicts and interests. She is drawn into this microcosm which seems to be a reflection of Cuban society today.
